flowchart LR
  %% Compounding Knowledge Loop (v1)

  A[Customer Intake] --> B[Scoping Inputs Captured]
  B --> C[AI Scope Draft]

  C --> D[Ops Review & Edits]
  D --> E[Scope Approved & Sent]

  E --> F[Work Executed]
  F --> G[Outcome Signals Captured]

  G --> H[Postmortem + Labeling]
  H --> I[Template & Prompt Updates]
  I --> J[Taxonomy & Routing Rules Updated]

  J --> C

  %% Governance + Instrumentation overlays
  K[(Trust / Governance Checks)] -.-> D
  L[(Instrumentation Events)] -.-> B
  L -.-> G
